org.dei.facts.parser

Class Transition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dei.facts.parser.Transition

  • public class Transition
extends java.lang.Object
    The Transition class represents a transition in a state machine. It contains the conditions that trigger the transition, the target state, and the name of the rule associated with the transition.
